(2373, 24344, 'Chapter 1 (第一章)', 'Elyzia''s debut Memento EP: Chapter 1 is a fusion of groovy rock chops and metal riffs layered with melodic vocals. From the dark and ambient ''爱太累'' to the head banging ''Monster'', the various influences of each member are evident and mercilessly poured into every track.\r\n\r\nAll songs from Elyzia can be heard on their official website & myspace once the demo recording is done and uploaded but the EP will also include the hardrocking ''Earthquake'', a track that had not been released before and ''Luna'', the instrumental that got Elyzia into the online dancing game Audition. Alot of re-recording and re-mastering work is also done for all the previous tracks.\r\n\r\nThe EP is co-produced, mixed and mastered by Rhea, Frankie, Ivor (Elyzia) with Ah Boy at TNT Music Productions. Design & photography works are done by Michel (Elyzia) & friends. Website is done by Rhea (Elyzia) and not to mention all songs are written and arranged by Elyzia. Emphasis on DIY is the cornerstone of Elyzia''s progress.\r\n\r\nAs this is the online version, it will not contain our english single ''Parasite'', which was featured on Asian Rock Rising Vol.39 and ''Earthquake''. For ordering the complete EP, check out their website (www.elyziaband.com) for information.', '2009-12-25 00:00:00', 0, 2, 1, 'K.K wong & Elyzia (一粒沙)', 'none', 0, '', 1, 0, '2010-02-10 11:00:16', '2015-02-16 15:47:24', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
